
***** VAR_IMAGE.inc *****

rule(s):
1. commande -> VAR_IMAGE '.' identifier

description:
if the identifier is the string "inc",
increments the image buffer position.


Example(s):

i.init
for x=0 to i.tx-1 {
  print "value at x = "; print x; print ": ";
  print i.val; print "\n";
  i.inc
}

